{"name":"AC Bonus (UMK)","type":"feat","img":"systems/pf1/icons/spells/fog-air-1.jpg","flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.pf1.class-abilities.MJbeCji2yK4omd80"},"pf1":{},"scene-packer":{"hash":"529289c102b0f451ae52a3e248769eaeea5e352b","sourceId":"Item.tSDvgbKeVafgd1Bc"}},"system":{"description":{"value":"<p>When unarmored and unencumbered, the monk adds his&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Wisdom-Wis-\">Wisdom</a>&nbsp;bonus (if any) to his&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Armor-class\">AC</a>&nbsp;and his&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Combat-Maneuver-Defense\">CMD</a>. In addition, a monk gains a +1 bonus to&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Armor-Class\">AC</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Combat-Maneuver-Defense\">CMD</a>&nbsp;at 4th level. This bonus increases by 1 for every four monk levels thereafter, up to a maximum of +5 at 20th level.</p>\n<p>These bonuses to&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Armor-Class\">AC</a>&nbsp;apply even against touch attacks or when the monk is&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/conditions#TOC-Flat-Footed\">flat-footed</a>. He loses these bonuses <span class=\"notImp\" title=\"Not Implemented\">when he is immobilized or&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/conditions#TOC-Helpless\">helpless</a></span>, when he wears any&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/glossary#TOC-Armor-Bonus\">armor</a>, when he carries a shield, or when he carries a medium or heavy load.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"actions":[{"_id":"w3grfd2lq2od3i5g","name":"Use","img":"systems/pf1/icons/spells/fog-air-1.jpg","description":"","tag":"","activation":{"cost":1,"type":"passive"},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"passive"}},"duration":{"value":null